I(X;Y) = \sum_{y \in Y} \sum_{x \in X}                   p(x,y) \log{ \left( \frac{p(x,y)}{p_1(x)\,p_2(y)}                               \right) }, \,\!
x_0
CI(x_0,Y) = \sum_{y \in Y} p(x_0,y) \log{ \left( \frac{p(x_0,y)}{p_1(x_0)\,p_2(y)}                               \right) }, \,\!
CI(x_0,Y) \ge 0
I(X;Y)\ge0
